OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry day but a few
OL,6,Fspots of light rain and drizzle
OL,7,Fpossible. Cloudy for most with a few
OL,8,Fbrief bright intervals breaking
OL,9,Fthrough. Moderate to fresh
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in the evening with a
OL,13,Flittle light rain possible. Remaining
OL,14,Fmostly cloudy overnight with some more
OL,15,Fpersistent rain and drizzle for Orkney
OL,16,Fand some clear intervals developing
OL,17,Ffor Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
