OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy over Orkney with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle. Drier
OL,7,Ffor Shetland with variable cloud and
OL,8,Fsome sunny intervals. Light
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,12,Fmixed few days with mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fconditions and outbreaks of rain, but
OL,14,Fthere will still be some drier and
OL,15,Fbrighter interludes. Strong winds at
OL,16,Ftimes Thursday and Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
